### API Gestor de Historias de Usuario
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### ==========================================
### RUTA DE PRUEBA
### ==========================================
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================
### SPRINTS
### ==========================================

### Listar todos los sprints
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sprints
Accept: application/json

### Ver un sprint específico
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sprints/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear un sprint
POST http://localhost:8000/api/sprints
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Sprint 1",
    "fecha_inicio": "2026-05-01",
    "fecha_fin": "2026-05-15"
}

### Editar un sprint
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/sprints/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nombre": "Sprint 1 Actualizado",
    "fecha_inicio": "2026-05-01",
    "fecha_fin": "2026-05-20"
}

### Eliminar un sprint
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/sprints/1
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================
### HISTORIAS DE USUARIO
### ==========================================

### Listar todas las historias
GET http://localhost:8000/api/historias
Accept: application/json

### Ver una historia específica
GET http://localhost:8000/api/historias/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear una historia
POST http://localhost:8000/api/historias
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "titulo": "Como usuario quiero iniciar sesión",
    "descripcion": "Implementar sistema de login con usuario y contraseña",
    "responsable": "Juan Pérez",
    "estado": "nueva",
    "puntos": 5,
    "fecha_creacion": "2026-05-10",
    "sprint_id": 1
}

### Editar una historia
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/historias/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "titulo": "Como usuario quiero iniciar sesión con Google",
    "estado": "activa",
    "puntos": 8
}

### Eliminar una historia
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/historias/1
Accept: application/json

### Listar historias de un sprint
GET http://localhost:8000/api/sprints/1/historias
Accept: application/json

### ==========================================
### INFORMES
### ==========================================

### Resumen por sprint
GET http://localhost:8000/api/informes/sprints
Accept: application/json

### Resumen por responsable
GET http://localhost:8000/api/informes/responsables
Accept: application/json
